snippet.title: AILA - Exclusive Announcement Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description:
Take a look at the debut trailer for AILA. Combining classic survival horror motives with science fiction, the game blurs the line between real and artificial, telling the story of an AI getting out of control and threatening the life of the protagonist, as well as everybody else. AILA is launching at a later date.

#IGN #Gaming
